    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Currency of Austria and Liechtenstein between 1919 and 1925; from after the dissolution of the Austro-Hungarian Empire until the introduction of the Schilling and the Franken, respectively. Intended to replace the Austro-Hungarian Krone, it was prone to hyperinflation and was replaced by the Austrian Schilling.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
